lead_paragraph: Jim Harbaugh is stumping for another Heisman Trophy candidate, shifting his lobbying efforts from Jabrill Peppers to Wilton Speight.

headline.print_headline: Wilton Speight Helps No. 2 Michigan Rout Maryland 59-3
